{
  "stem": "894.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were sitting there, with our hearts pounding, because we didn't know if a German observed and is coming after us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Nobody came after us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I wouldn't even guarantee that one of them saw us and didn't care.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He had one less to worry about.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That is a possibility.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I have no way of knowing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I looked in, and I see in a crib, a large kitchen [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that has windows to the front and then a bedroom, and a young woman standing by window, looking, in the bedroom.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The kid is in the crib, in the kitchen, screaming and screaming.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we stayed crouched, there, on the floor, for a little while.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But then we were still scared that they will follow us and find us there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So we opened-- the door was open, and we came in to the kitchen and closed the door, figuring if the Germans come looking, they will not see us outside.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And, of course, I don't have to tell you, the baby didn't welcome us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He started to scream, until the mother came to see what happened.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "What was interesting. though, when she walked in, I recall, she sees two strangers, and she didn't act surprised.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I think she immediately connected that we dropped off from this line, because she was watching them, and we looked, uh-- dressed as elegantly [LAUGHS] and as beautiful as they were.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she assumed, but she didn't act.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what was also very interesting, that she took a big loaf of bread, and she cut two pieces of bread.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she handed it one to each of us, literally without saying anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember that I'm standing here.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
